Pace is the time a runner needs to run one kilometer or one mile.
That is, pace means minutes per kilometer or minutes per mile.
Many training sessions work with pace as a measure and a unit for training control. 
The skyPacer pace calculator app allows you to calculate pace based on the distance, speed and duration of an activity.
